    <h3>🗺️ NT Road Tip</h3>
    <p>The Central Arnhem Road from Katherine to Nhulunbuy is approximately 700 km — plan extra fuel stops as remote stations can be scarce.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3>⛽ NT Fuel Prices</h3>
    <p>Fuel prices in remote NT can be significantly higher than Darwin or Alice Springs. Budget an extra 20–40¢/L for outback travel.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3>🛻 4WD Tip</h3>
    <p>Many NT tracks require a 4WD vehicle. Fuel efficiency drops on unsealed roads — increase your estimate by 15–20% for dirt tracks.</p>
  </div>
